<p>更多语法参考：<a href="https://knsv.github.io/mermaid/#flowcharts-basic-syntax" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mermaid 流程图语法参考</a></p>
<h3><span id="11-mermaid-序列图">11. Mermaid 序列图</span></h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Alice-&gt;John: Hello John, how are you?</span><br><span class="line">loop every minute</span><br><span class="line">    John--&gt;Alice: Great!</span><br><span class="line">end</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
